Series by Tamora Pierce quiz
[INS::INS]
Fun Trivia

This quiz is dedicated to all the series, well, most of them, by Tamora Pierce. They are: "The Song of the Lioness", "The
Immortals", and "The Circle of Magic".

Average score for this quiz is 7 / 10. Difficulty: Average. Played 2,127 times. As of Nov 29 17.
1. The series take place in which places?

( ) Galla and Scanra
( ) Tortall and Benden
( ) Copper Isles and Tortall
( ) Tortall and Summersea


